OL,5,G0100 Outback Truckers
OL,6,     FJeff Fulwood takes on one of the
OL,7,     Fmost notorious roads in Australia
OL,8,     Fto deliver a vital supply run to a
OL,9,     Fremote community; the only problem
OL,10,     F- it's missing an essential load.
OL,11,G0200 Trucking Hell
OL,12,     FA bin lorry has come off a country
OL,13,     Flane, its wheels slipping in mud,
OL,14,     Fand a box van trailer with has
OL,15,     Fbeen uncoupled and left with the
OL,16,     Ffront supported solely by its
OL,17,     FLanding Legs.
